    question: "How to make website responsive?",
    answer: "**Responsive Web Design Techniques:**\n\n**1. Viewport Meta Tag:**\n```html\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n```\n\n**2. Fluid Grid System:**\n```css\n.container {\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.col {\n    float: left;\n    width: 100%;\n}\n\n@media (min-width: 768px) {\n    .col { width: 50%; }\n}\n\n@media (min-width: 1024px) {\n    .col { width: 33.33%; }\n}\n```\n\n**3. Flexible Images:**\n```css\nimg, video, iframe {\n    max-width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n}\n```\n\n**4. Media Queries:**\n```css\n/* Mobile First Approach */\n/* Base styles for mobile */\n.element {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    padding: 10px;\n}\n\n/* Tablet */\n@media (min-width: 768px) {\n    .element {\n        font-size: 16px;\n        padding: 15px;\n    }\n}\n\n/* Desktop */\n@media (min-width: 1024px) {\n    .element {\n        font-size: 18px;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n}\n\n/* Desktop First Approach */\n@media (max-width: 1024px) { /* Tablet styles */ }\n@media (max-width: 768px) { /* Mobile styles */ }\n```\n\n**5. Flexbox:**\n```css\n.nav {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n}\n\n@media (min-width: 768px) {\n    .nav {\n        flex-direction: row;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**6. CSS Grid:**\n```css\n.grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    gap: 20px;\n}\n\n@media (min-width: 768px) {\n    .grid {\n        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    }\n}\n\n@media (min-width: 1024px) {\n    .grid {\n        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**7. Responsive Typography:**\n```css\nhtml {\n    font-size: 16px;\n}\n\n@media (min-width: 768px) {\n    html {\n        font-size: 18px;\n    }\n}\n\n/* Fluid typography */\n.title {\n    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);\n}\n```\n\n**8. Relative Units:**\n```css\n/* Use REM, EM, %, vw, vh */\n.container {\n    width: 90%;\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    padding: 1rem;\n}\n\n.hero {\n    height: 100vh;  /* Full viewport height */\n    font-size: 2rem;\n}\n```\n\n**9. Responsive Navigation:**\n```css\n/* Hamburger menu for mobile */\n.nav-menu {\n    display: none;\n}\n\n.menu-toggle {\n    display: block;\n}\n\n@media (min-width: 768px) {\n    .nav-menu {\n        display: flex;\n    }\n    .menu-toggle {\n        display: none;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**10. Testing:**\n• Chrome DevTools device emulation\n• Real device testing\n• BrowserStack for cross-browser\n• Lighthouse for performance",
